oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Shouse family home
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of the Shouse family home located on Shipp's Bend. Men, women, and children are sitting on the front porch. Chickens are seen on the grass in front of the home.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Houses; Porches; Chickens
